OL,3,CNHS apologises to psychiatric unit
OL,4,Cchild abuse victims
OL,6,FA health board has issued a "full and
OL,7,Funreserved apology" to victims of
OL,8,Fhistorical child abuse at a
OL,9,Fpsychiatric unit in Dumfries.
OL,11,FLadyfield, a former children's
OL,12,Fresidential psychiatric unit which was
OL,13,Fpreviously run by NHS Dumfries and
OL,14,FGalloway, has come under scrutiny by
OL,15,Fthe long-running Scottish Child Abuse
OL,16,FInquiry.
OL,18,FIn an update published in an NHS
OL,19,FDumfries and Galloway report in
OL,20,FDecember, the NHS board chief
