OL,3,CNHS apologises to psychiatric unit
OL,4,Cchild abuse victims
OL,6,Fexecutive said conditions children and
OL,7,Fyoung people experienced at the estate
OL,8,Fwere "totally unacceptable".
OL,10,FAn apology was issued on behalf of the
OL,11,Fhealth board to the Scottish Child
OL,12,FAbuse Inquiry and affected individuals.
OL,14,FA health board representative
OL,15,Fdescribed the abuse as "deeply
OL,16,Ftroubling" in the report, and said
OL,17,Fthat the board was ready to assist the
OL,18,Fpolice and the Crown Office in any
OL,19,Fcriminal investigations which might
OL,20,Fresult.
