OL,6,FThe update detailed in the report
OL,7,Fadded that NHS Dumfries and Galloway
OL,8,Fno longer provides inpatient mental
OL,9,Fhealth care facilities, with services
OL,10,Fnow accessed through the new
OL,11,FChildren's Hospital and Skye House,
OL,12,Foperated by NHS Greater Glasgow and
OL,13,FClyde.
OL,15,FClinicians will maintain
OL,16,Fresponsibility for children and young
OL,17,Fpeople who seek treatment outside of
OL,18,FNHS Dumfries and Galloway, the update
OL,19,Fadded.
OL,21,FLadyfield closed in 2001.
